{
  "stem": "17625.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 133.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they burned them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because the whole thing they had to open up and-- and-- the whole thing and-- and burn them again, and start burning them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But later on, this kommando was part of the-- was the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were only a few.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they learned the trade too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They learned the trade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, the-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] were the-- the first ones which they were-- schleppers, there was a lot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what it mean, schleppers?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schleppers are all you had to do are-- is a belt from-- from-- from the pants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And put them on the hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you schlep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All by the feet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the way that they-- they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and to-- they pulled-- they had to pour water, it should be slippery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was before they brought them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had to take him to cut the hair, and cut-- take out the teeth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they bring him there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they built, also, four and five.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the same-- where one-- two and three was, a little bit further up, near the forest was a little [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They built another two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was assigned to the four and five.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four and five.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, there was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was two kapos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was Leizer kapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one was Schlomo, Schlomo kapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was with Leizer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- he was a-- a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, Bialystok, there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- then at five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then at five.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beginning at four, then at five.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coming there-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they were-- we worked there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had steady, steady supply.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one guy-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the SS scharfuhrer, Quackernack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- we called him the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
